<!-- ============================================ 
  Síntesis de la lección (discusión de cierre)
=================================================  -->
<subsubsection xml:id="lec-estimarYMedirPesos-sintesis" component="profesor">
  <shorttitle><custom ref="synthesis-leccion-titulo"/></shorttitle>
  <title><custom ref="synthesis-leccion-titulo"/></title>
  <title component="profesor"><nbsp/>(5 mins)</title>

  <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
  <p><q>¿En qué casos es suficiente estimar el peso y no es necesario conocer el peso exacto?</q> (To know if something is too heavy to pick up. When we're just curious about how much something weighs. When we’re buying something like fruit by the gram or kilogram and want to get an idea of how much it would cost.)</p>

</subsubsection>



